org.zeromq.api

Class Message.Frame

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.zeromq.api.Message.Frame
  • Enclosing class:
    Message

    public static class Message.Frame
extends Object
    Represents a single frame of data within a message. Instances of this class are immutable.
